      "text": "es pazeblolhs us manneem Zek-keem/un us mannahm Rohkahin.\n1. Un wiꞥſch fazzija usman:\nDaniſel tu peemihligs Wihrs/nemm wehrd tohs Wahrdus/ ko-es us tew runnaſchn / un zelleesi-stahwu/ jo taggad eſnu es pee-tewi fuhtihts. Un kad wiꞥſch to-Wahrdü ar mannim runnaja / tad zehlohs es tribzedans."
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "12. Tad fazzija wiꞥſch us-man : Ne bihſtees Daniſel/ jo no-tahs pirmas Deenas/ kad tu ar-tawu Sirdi effi dewees to fa-prast/un effi tewi mehrdejs tawa-Deewa Breekscha / tad irr tawi-Wahrdi paklanftiti / un es efmu-tawu Wahrdü deht atnahzis."
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "13. Tomehr tahs Persexu-Walstibas Leels-Kungs stahwe-ja man pretti diwidejmits un-weenu Deenu/ un rangi/ Mif-kelts tas pirmajs no teim pirma-jeem Leel-Kungeem nahze man-par Paligu/ tad ustwarreju es-tur pee teem Persexu Kebnizseem."
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "14. Nu efmu es nahzis tew-Sinku doht no ta/ kas taweem-Laudim nahkoſcha Latka notiks/ jo wehl fchi Parahdiſchana pehz-ugu Laiku notiks."
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "15. Un kad wiꞥſch fchohs-Wahrdus ar mannim runnaja/-tad ſkattiju es ar farvu Waign-pee Seimmes/un paltkku kluſtu."
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "16. Un raugt/ weens/ kas Zil-weka Behrneem lihds bija/ ais-kahre mannas Luhpas. Tad at-darrju es farvu Mutti/ un faz-ziju us to/ kas pee mannim stah-"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "weja: Mans Kungs / pahr fcho-Parahdiſchannu drebb manni Łoh-zekti/ ka man ne kahds Spehks-paleek.\n17. Un ka warr fcha manna-Kunga Kalps ar fcho mannu-Kungu runnaht/ jo noſchi Laika-ne paleek ne kahds Spehks pee-mannim/ un man arri ne kahdq-Dwascha atleek."
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "18. Tad aiskahre mann atkak-weens / kam Zilweka Gihmis-bija/un spehzinaja manni."
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "19. Un wiꞥſch fazzija : Ne-bihſtees/ tu peememings Wihrs/paleez ar Meereu/ un ſtiprinajees/ſtiprinajees. Un kamehr wiꞥſch-ar mannim runnaja / palikku es-ſtipraks/ un fazzija : Runna-mans Kungs / jo tu effi manni-ſtiprinajs."
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "20. Tad fazzija wiꞥſch : Sin-nti tu/ kapehz es pee tew eſnu-nahzis? bet nu greesitchohs es at-pakkat/ ar to Persexu Leel-Kun-gu kaxroht/ un kad es buhſchu-iegahjs/ tad nahks to Greekeru-Leels-Kungs."
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "21. Bet es stahſtischu tew to/-kas eekſch pateefuem Raksteem-usraſſihts irr/ un neweens irr/-kas man prett winneem spehzina/ ka ween juhu Leels-Kungs-Mikkels."
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "1. Un es eſnu (tas pats)/kas pirmā Gaddā Darijs ta-Meedera pee winna stahweja/winzu spehzinaht un ſtiprinaht."
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "2. Un es stahſtischu tew to-Pateefibu."
    }
  ],
